report.title: With Bi Polar Disorder
report.author: Jussipupu
report.bodytext: I'll keep this short and sweet. Methoxetamine does nothing to me, even if I take high dosages IV. With my friends it is a nice party drug when in a dance place with music and lights because it tends to trigger synesthesia and in that sort of environment people don't get too freaked out. /n /n For me, though, it seems to put me in an active mood and bring me out of the depression part of my bi-polar disorder. /n /n I take Seroquel and Lamictal. Perhaps that interaction causes this effect on me.
